Subject: x86/dma: Get rid of iommu_pass_through
Git-commit: c53c47aac4ff9509e7e1a32666baefbd9793c5a0
Patch-mainline: v5.4-rc1
References: bsc#1160320

This variable has no users anymore. Remove it and tell the
IOMMU code via its new functions about requested DMA modes.

Reviewed-by: Borislav Petkov <bp@suse.de>
Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
